dataProducts.description: The 17.3” FHD Gaming Notebook from Gateway is the ultimate portable notebook that brings crystal-clear picture for all of your tasks. You'll be immersed in sound where your movies, TV shows, video games and music happen all around you, not just in front of you. The computer is powered by 11th Gen Intel® Core™ i7-11800H Processor and has 16 GB memory RAM.
bulletPoints: Intel® Core™ i7-11800H Processor, Up to 4.60 GHz
17.3” LCD IPS FHD Display, (1920 x 1080), 120Hz Refresh Rate
Includes 1-month Xbox Game Pass for PC*
